# 1. HRMS Application

A Human Resource Management System designed to simplify employee operations and internal company workflows.

## Features
- Employee Dashboard
- Leave Management
- Holiday Calendar
- Attendance Management
- Attendance Regularization
- Notifications & Alerts
- Technical Support Module
- Employee Profile Management

## Tech Stack
- Flutter
- REST APIs
- Backend Integration

